eqnarray:
\begin{eqnarray}
F_{\mu\nu} & = & \partial_\mu A_\nu - \partial_\nu A_\mu - i g\left[ A_\mu 
, A_\nu \right] \, , \nonumber \\
D_\mu \Phi & = & \left( \partial_\mu - i g A_\mu \right)\Phi \, , \nonumber 
\\
A_\mu & = & A_{\mu}^a \frac{\tau^a}{2} \, , 
\label{covariant}
\

\begin{eqnarray}
{\mathcal L}_H^{\rm (ct)} & = & 
c_1\mbox{tr}\left(F^{\mu\nu}F_{\mu\nu}\right) + 
c_2\mbox{tr}\left(\left[D^{\mu}\Phi\right]^{\dag}D_{\mu}\Phi\right )
\nonumber \\ & & +\ 
c_3\left[\mbox{tr}\left(\Phi^{\dag}\Phi\right)-2v^2 \right] + 
c_4\left[\mbox{tr}\left(\Phi^{\dag}\Phi\right)-2v^2\right]^2 \, .
\label{Lct}
\

\begin{eqnarray}
E_{\rm vac} & = & -\frac{1}{2}\sum_j D_j|\epsilon_j| 
- \frac{1}{2}\int_0^\infty dk \sqrt{k^2+m_f^2} 
\left( \Delta\rho(k) - \sum_{i=1}^{N}\Delta\rho^{(i)}(k)\right) 
\nonumber\\ & &  
+ \sum_{i=1}^N E_{\rm FD}^{(i)} + E_{\rm ct} \, .
\

\begin{eqnarray}
A_i (\vec{x}) & = & -A^i(\vec{x})=\frac{1}{2g}\left[ a_1(r)\tau_j\hat{x}_j\hat{x}_i + 
\frac{\alpha(r)}{r}(\tau_i - \tau_j\hat{x}_j\hat{x}_i ) + 
\frac{\gamma(r)}{r}\epsilon_{ijk}\hat{x}_j\tau_k \right] \, , 
\nonumber \\
\Phi (\vec{x}) & = & v \left[ s(r) + ip(r)\tau_j\hat{x}_j \right] \, ,
\label{SphericalAnsatz}
\

\begin{eqnarray}
\rho(0) & = & 1 \, , \nonumber \\
\rho'(0) & = & 0 \, , \nonumber \\
\theta(0) & = & -2n_{\theta}\pi \, , \nonumber \\ 
a_1(0) & = & \theta '(0) \, ,  \nonumber \\
\mbox{either } \Sigma(0) & = & 0 \mbox{ or } \eta(0) = -n_{\eta}\pi \, .
\label{BoundCond0}
\

\begin{eqnarray}
\rho(r)&=&1\, , \quad \Sigma(r)=1 \, , \nonumber \\
\theta(r)&=&f^{(n)}(r)\, , \quad
\eta(r)=\frac{f^{(n)}(r)}{2}\, , \quad
a_1(r)=f^{(n)\prime}(r)\, .
\label{Vacua1D}
\

\begin{eqnarray}
N_{\rm CS} & = & -\frac{g^2}{8\pi^2}\epsilon_{ijk}\int d^3x 
\mbox{tr} \left(A_i\partial_jA_k-\frac{2}{3}igA_iA_jA_k  \right) 
\nonumber \\
& = & \frac{1}{2\pi}\int_0^\infty dr 
\left[a_1+\rho^2(\theta^\prime - a_1)\right] \, .
\

\begin{eqnarray}
\eta & = & -\pi e^{-r/w} + p_0 \frac{r/w}{1+(r/w)^2}e^{-r/w} \, , \nonumber \\
\Sigma & = & 1 + p_1 \frac{1}{1+(r/w)}e^{-r/w} \, , \nonumber \\
a_1 & = & p_2 \frac{r/w}{1+(r/w)^2}e^{-r/w} \, , \nonumber \\
\rho & = & 1 + p_3 \frac{(r/w)^2}{1+(r/w)^3}e^{-r/w} \, , 
\

\begin{eqnarray}
D_G(r) & = & \mbox{{\sf 1}\mbox{\hspace*{-0.16em}}\rule{0.04em}{1.55ex}\mbox{\hspace*{0.1em}}} \left( \frac{\partial^2}{\partial r^2} +
\frac{2}{r}\frac{\partial}{\partial r} + k^2 \right) - \frac{1}{r^2}O_G \,
, \cr\cr
O_G & = & {\rm diag}\left((G+1)(G+2), G(G+1), G(G+1), (G-1)G\right)\, ,
\
